		<wp:meta_key><![CDATA[translations_en_content]]></wp:meta_key>
		<wp:meta_value><![CDATA[<p><img src=\"https://mobile-cms.univ-lorraine.fr/assets/85653b13-c602-408b-b519-d0b5df91500d?width=50&amp;height=45\" alt=\" Ully\"></p>\n<h2>Mail, contacts and calendar synchronization</h2>\n<p>For even greater ease of use, your Zimbra university e-mail system can be integrated with your smartphone's native applications.</p>\n<p>To configure this, follow the <a href=\"https://wikidocs.univ-lorraine.fr/x/2gQ1Aw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">guide</a>.</p>\n<h2>Configuring wifi networks</h2>\n<p>You have a single wifi network on all your campuses and CROUS. The easiest way to configure your connection is to use the configurator. You will find all the explanations here : <a href=\"https://wikidocs.univ-lorraine.fr/display/DNDoc/Configurateur+WiFi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Documentation</a></p>\n<h2>Lost / reset password</h2>\n<p>You need to reset your password following an incident such as account theft, or you've simply forgotten your login or password. Go to the <a href=\"https://sesame.univ-lorraine.fr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sesame</a> application.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Finally, don't hesitate to contact our Ully chatbot, accessible from the menu at the bottom of this application.</p>]]></wp:meta_value>
