		<wp:meta_value><![CDATA[<p><img src=\"https://mobile-cms.univ-lorraine.fr/assets/6a805a1d-8b8f-402b-b4fe-70be6460461f?width=230&amp;height=191\" alt=\"Mesri Cmjn\"></p>\n<p>The&nbsp;<strong>UnivLorraine</strong> application was developed using <strong>Esup-Multi</strong>, an open source project supported by the <a href=\"https://www.esup-portail.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Esup-portail consortium</a>.</p>\n<p>Initiated by the Universit&eacute; de Lorraine, in collaboration with other institutions, this project aims to meet the specific needs of the university community, while offering a solution that can be adapted and customised for each institution.</p>\n<p>Multi, part-funded by the <strong>France Relance </strong>plan as part of the call for <strong>Services Num&eacute;riques aux &Eacute;tudiants</strong> projects, offers a modular architecture enabling extensive customisation, ensuring that the Esup-Multi application can interconnect with the institution's information system.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://mobile-cms.univ-lorraine.fr/assets/4b40ea3a-afeb-4546-82c7-a90609cf5727?width=417&amp;height=91\" alt=\"Etiquette   Crop\"></p>]]></wp:meta_value>
